1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:07,000
Shame I must greet you in this bitter cold without a hearty drink.

2
00:00:09,000 --> 00:00:15,000
It's no easy feat getting here. I know you didn't come to keep me company.

3
00:00:19,000 --> 00:00:28,000
In your heart there must be something you can't get over, or someone you can't let go of.

4
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:39,000
Same goes for me. I can't kill that monkey. No one can, except himself.

5
00:00:40,000 --> 00:00:52,000
But at last I see this is the only way. He had no choice, and neither did I.

